mo\"}]},{\"name\":\"places/ChIJURDKN2eAhYARN0AMzUEaiKo/photos/AdCG2DNzM14eAnNdRqKEegHOsAxvvbCZyFFVbl2t9fEfA0oK70lfUUpTQBCkRRgfS2liqYNQVFwk4IH2wRzZVnoj3b5gx4WJlfDPSnGGQlyqrfdh-qkk8krZW_YAxHGdf1ExBb5Dyo7tfyQJuljJMrzZqoVYUitZSHwNjsMT\",\"widthPx\":4080,\"heightPx\":3072,\"authorAttributions\":[{\"displayName\":\"Andrés Ornelas\",\"uri\":\"https://maps.google.com/maps/contrib/107667037368655383825\",\"photoUri\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUB8Zh2m8YcwxUbOed3xMU1w5l_buM2e3ZNE2hAlo71b8CilkAdJQ=s100-p-k-no-mo\"}]},{\"name\":\"places/ChIJURDKN2eAhYARN0AMzUEaiKo/photos/AdCG2DPDI1MSQQiqPhJaT4ixM5X3rfMEfrgLJr4TASz9tPtAtMi2KZ31tnz3ifLGv5AKY9KL9Q-CAlzfoYIOGBtGvQPEEx4_mvjFbrR9-GacNov4Rh4FUPQ6R9kckmJuumk3Z1WhQtnxF2NOApAZzC8MfxETtibFl9Q0IC44\",\"widthPx\":2992,\"heightPx\":2992,\"authorAttributions\":[{\"displayName\":\"Vol Tron\",\"uri\":\"https://maps.google.com/maps/contrib/116310692803943272547\",\"photoUri\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUFJikZUbrnH7HmOvz06Es1XetdbFPe-ju6kr9Qvuwq2ufNyg6C=s100-p-k-no-mo\"}]}],\"outdoorSeating\":true,\"liveMusic\":false,\"menuForChildren\":false,\"servesCocktails\":true,\"servesDessert\":true,\"servesCoffee\":true,\"goodForChildren\":false,\"allowsDogs\":false,\"restroom\":true,\"goodForGroups\":true,\"goodForWatchingSports\":false,\"paymentOptions\":{\"acceptsCreditCards\":true,\"acceptsDebitCards\":true,\"acceptsCashOnly\":false,\"acceptsNfc\":true},\"parkingOptions\":{\"paidParkingLot\":true,\"paidStreetParking\":true,\"valetParking\":false},\"accessibilityOptions\":{\"wheelchairAccessibleParking\":false,\"wheelchairAccessibleEntrance\":true,\"wheelchairAccessibleRestroom\":true,\"wheelchairAccessibleSeating\":true},\"generativeSummary\":{\"overview\":{\"text\":\"Expansive, waterfront Peruvian restaurant serving ceviche and other seafood dishes, plus cocktails.\",\"languageCode\":\"en-US\"},\"description\":{\"text\":\"Upscale Peruvian eatery set on Pier 1 1/2 in the Embarcadero neighborhood with bay views.\\nThe large venue features a bar and outdoor seating on the waterfront patio. It's popular for lunch and dinner, and reservations are recommended. People say the staff is attentive.\\nThe menu focuses on seafood. Popular dishes include empanadas, ceviche, and lomo saltado. Guests also like the pisco sours and the desserts.\\nVisitors praise the location, the atmosphere, and the views.\\nCustomers typically spend $50–100.\",\"languageCode\":\"en-US\"},\"references\":{\"reviews\":[{\"name\":\"places/ChIJURDKN2eAhYARN0AMzUEaiKo/reviews/ChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUN4OWF6bVZ3EAE\",\"relativePublishTimeDescription\":\"prije godinu dana\",\"rating\":4,\"text\":{\"text\":\"Nevjerojatna lokacija, hrana može biti bolja, ali općenito mi se jako sviđa ovo mjesto.\",\"languageCode\":\"hr-HR\"},\"originalText\":{\"text\":\"Amazing location, food can be better but overall I like this place a lot.\",\"languageCode\":\"en\"},\"authorAttribution\":{\"displayName\":\"Haluk\",\"uri\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/105086799620435041519/reviews\",\"photoUri\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjURRJcN2RkuYV6wb43YSha5yQu52Ydwud_woxHWKpx71Vl8eXYrlw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5\"},\"publishTime\":\"2023-05-22T22:59:25.676845Z\"},{\"name\":\"places/ChIJURDKN2eAhYARN0AMzUEaiKo/reviews/ChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUNKX0tTeUNBEAE\",\"relativePublishTimeDescription\":\"prije godinu dana\",\"rating\":4,\"text\":{\"text\":\"Došao sam ovamo na timsku večeru i apsolutno su mi se svidjeli ceviche i pulpo.  Mjesto je bilo živo i brujalo je od razgovora.  Usluga je bila vrlo pažljiva i dobro se brinula o nama.\\n\\nOpćenito, svakako bih preporučio za grupni događaj ili čak sastanak 1:1 ako vam ne smeta malo glasnije.\",\"languageCode\":\"hr-HR\"},\"originalText\":{\"text\":\"Came here for a team dinner and absolutely loved the ceviche and pulpo.  The place was alive and buzzing with conversations.  The service was very attentive and took good care of us.\\n\\nOverall, would definitely recommend for a group event or even a 1:1 date if you don’t mind a little loudness.\",\"languageCode\":\"en\"},\"authorAttribution\":{\"displayName\":\"Raul Ricano\",\"uri\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/115377573808281937078/reviews\",\"photoUri\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW7z-EVdhnNfUWXtxnJJ6cO3uvA-NTzwlW6yxWnQ0HVoJ_93ZRq=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5\"},\"publishTime\":\"2023-06-23T06:30:56.108781Z\"},{\"name\":\"places/ChIJURDKN2eAhYARN0AMzUEaiKo/reviews/ChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSURKNE1fY2VREAE\",\"relativePublishTimeDescription\":\"prije godinu dana\",\"rating\":5,\"text\":{\"text\":\"Hrana: Ostao sam bez riječi. Usluga: topla, pažljiva i brza. Viči Carlosu, daj mu povišicu!! Atmosfera: doslovno na SF zaljevu na vodi. Znam kako postaješ bolji od ovoga. Iskreno, moj omiljeni restoran u Bay Areau i moram ga posjetiti!!!!\",\"languageCode\":\"hr-HR\"},\"originalText\":{\"text\":\"The food: I am speechless. The service: warm attentive and quick. Shout out to Carlos, give him a raise!! The atmosphere: literally on SF bay on the water. Idk how you get better than this. Honestly my favorite restaurant in the Bay Area and a must go!!!!\",\"languageCode\":\"en\"},\"authorAttribution\":{\"displayName\":\"Jaci S\",\"uri\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/103871899613318940203/reviews\",\"photoUri\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV7HeG_tXo-mqWMoXshDCxaf_IOktxAmeblrfcP8V05L2bsS5T8kg=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3\"},\"publishTime\":\"2023-07-09T02:19:05.285806Z\"},{\"name\":\"places/ChIJURDKN2eAhYARN0AMzUEaiKo/reviews/ChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUN4OEtiUzlnRRAB\",\"relativePublishTimeDescription\":\"prije godinu dana\",\"rating\":5,\"text\":{\"text\":\"Najbolje mjesto za kvalitetan cebichi\",\"languageCode\":\"hr-HR\"},\"originalText\":{\"text\":\"Best place for quality cebichi\",\"languageCode\":\"en\"},\"authorAttribution\":{\"displayName\":\"adrian tout\",\"uri\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/114366982402710835599/reviews\",\"photoUri\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXvEvhHGJp___9TyVePqIRWWq8l6tQX7PbVhvxQ2jmzkj9zGABa2A=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3\"},\"publishTime\":\"2023-05-09T04:24:37.619431Z\"},{\"name\":\"places/ChIJURDKN2eAhYARN0AMzUEaiKo/reviews/ChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUR4OWNTbHVnRRAB\",\"relativePublishTimeDescription\":\"prije godinu dana\",\"rating\":5,\"text\":{\"text\":\"Hrana je bila nevjerojatna. Unatoč tome koliko su bili zaposleni, poslužitelj se uvijek brinuo o nama. Pustit ću da slike govore same za sebe. Ljubitelji hrane spremaju se zaljubiti se u peruanskoj avanturi. Provjerite jeste li gladni i također rezervirajte unaprijed. Ovo mjesto je prometno s razlogom. Uživati!\",\"languageCode\":\"hr-HR\"},\"originalText\":{\"text\":\"The food was amazing. Despite how busy they were, the server was always making sure we were taken care of. I will let the pictures speak for itself. Food lovers get ready to fall in love in a Peruvian adventure. Make sure you are hungry and also make a reservation in advance. This place is busy for a reason. Enjoy!\",\"languageCode\":\"en\"},\"authorAttribution\":{\"displayName\":\"Carlos Rodriguez (EastBayHomes)\",\"uri\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/104769287029377054778/reviews\",\"photoUri\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXSneIqxQ2ioKuxO9-uvbqMIHBBYhnV3kGXlHCVFlvmgQmJEza4Ww=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5\"},\"publishTime\":\"2023-06-13T00:54:32.431986Z\"}]}},\"addressDescriptor\":{\"landmarks\":[{\"name\":\"places/ChIJzVewMSeBhYAR1kYITFLiAL4\",\"placeId\":\"ChIJzVewMSeBhYAR1kYITFLiAL4\",\"displayName\":{\"text\":\"Pier 3\",\"languageCode\":\"en\"},\"types\":[\"establishment\",\"point_of_interest\",\"tourist_attraction\"],\"spatialRelationship\":\"AROUND_THE_CORNER\",\"straightLineDistanceMeters\":66.62422,\"travelDistanceMeters\":80.76846},{\"name\":\"places/ChIJWTGPjmaAhYARxz6l1hOj92w\",\"placeId\":\"ChIJWTGPjmaAhYARxz6l1hOj92w\",\"displayName\":{\"text\":\"Ferry Building\",\"languageCode\":\"en\"},\"types\":[\"establishment\"