\",\"petak: 16:00 – 21:00\",\"subota: Zatvoreno\",\"nedjelja: Zatvoreno\"],\"secondaryHoursType\":\"HAPPY_HOUR\"}],\"regularSecondaryOpeningHours\":[{\"openNow\":false,\"periods\":[{\"open\":{\"day\":2,\"hour\":16,\"minute\":0},\"close\":{\"day\":2,\"hour\":21,\"minute\":0}},{\"open\":{\"day\":3,\"hour\":16,\"minute\":0},\"close\":{\"day\":3,\"hour\":21,\"minute\":0}},{\"open\":{\"day\":4,\"hour\":16,\"minute\":0},\"close\":{\"day\":4,\"hour\":21,\"minute\":0}},{\"open\":{\"day\":5,\"hour\":16,\"minute\":0},\"close\":{\"day\":5,\"hour\":21,\"minute\":0}}],\"weekdayDescriptions\":[\"ponedjeljak: Zatvoreno\",\"utorak: 16:00 – 21:00\",\"srijeda: 16:00 – 21:00\",\"četvrtak: 16:00 – 21:00\",\"petak: 16:00 – 21:00\",\"subota: Zatvoreno\",\"nedjelja: Zatvoreno\"],\"secondaryHoursType\":\"HAPPY_HOUR\"}],\"primaryType\":\"chinese_restaurant\",\"shortFormattedAddress\":\"Four Embarcadero Center, 4 Embarcadero Ctr Level, San Francisco\",\"editorialSummary\":{\"text\":\"Contemporary, family-style outlet serving Cantonese-style dishes with panoramic harbor views.\",\"languageCode\":\"en\"},\"reviews\":[{\"name\":\"places/ChIJZ1SMEQeBhYAR8Y0suKMr48o/reviews/ChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUNIaWZmSU5nEAE\",\"relativePublishTimeDescription\":\"prije mjesec dana\",\"rating\":5,\"text\":{\"text\":\"Odlučili smo ovdje ugostiti našu prijemnu večeru zbog prikladne lokacije, izvrsne hrane i lijepog pogleda sa zgradom trajekta u pozadini. Rezervirali smo pola prostora za večeru i vanjsku terasu za noćnu zabavu.\\n\\nTiffany je bila naš koordinator događaja i nevjerojatna je! Sve je jasno objasnila i javila nam se na vrijeme. Osoblje na večeri bilo je vrlo strpljivo tijekom cijelog događaja oko 22:00. Usluga je broj 1. Menadžer bara me čak zamolio da se na kraju s njim slikam. Bio sam jako iznenađen kvalitetom koktela ovdje. Svidjeli su mi se barmeni i super su brzo pripremali pića. Stol za desert bio je lijep dodatak. Nemam pritužbi, ali gomilu komplementa o kvaliteti hrane. Kako su svježe i kako su ukusne.\",\"languageCode\":\"hr-HR\"},\"originalText\":{\"text\":\"We decided to host our reception dinner here because of the convenient location, amazing food, and a nice view with ferry building as the background. We reserved half of the dinner area and the outdoor patio for the party at night.\\n\\nTiffany was our event coordinator and she's amazing! She explained everything clearly and got back to us in a timely manner. Staffs at the dinner was very very patient throughout the whole event ~10pm. The service is #1. The manager of the bar even asked me to take a shot with him at the end. I was very surprised by the quality of the cocktail here. I loved the bartenders and they made the drinks super quick. The dessert table was a nice touch. I got no complains but tons of complements about the quality of the food. How fresh and how yummy they are.\",\"languageCode\":\"en\"},\"authorAttribution\":{\"displayName\":\"Siulung Ng (Michael)\",\"uri\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/102403605275035233808/reviews\",\"photoUri\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUhMY9eP727t-_Ctx4EOIL3ojvryAcRVJw1SjpVual--1E-wwHlbg=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3\"},\"publishTime\":\"2024-09-06T06:46:24.050210Z\"},{\"name\":\"places/ChIJZ1SMEQeBhYAR8Y0suKMr48o/reviews/ChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSURuLWZtNnBBRRAB\",\"relativePublishTimeDescription\":\"prije 2 tjedna\",\"rating\":5,\"text\":{\"text\":\"Išla sam na užinu s ulaskom.\\nUkrasi su lijepi.\\n\\nVrhunac su PEČENE SVINJSKE PEČICE.\\nPreporučam svima da probaju ovo! To je obavezno!\\n\\nSiu mai je također ukusan. Unutra je sočan.\\nSve što sam naručio bilo je dobro osim jednog jelovnika koji je bio prefinjen u pikantnom umaku. Po mom mišljenju bilo je u redu, ali još nije izvrsno.\\n\\nU svakom slučaju to mi je najbolji dim sum do sada u Kaliforniji.\",\"languageCode\":\"hr-HR\"},\"originalText\":{\"text\":\"I went for brunch with walk-in.\\nThe decorations are nice.\\n\\nThe highlight is BAKED BBQ PORK BUNS.\\nI recommend everyone to try this! It’s a must!\\n\\nSiu mai is also delicious. It’s juicy inside.\\nEverything that I ordered was good except one menu which was wonton in spicy sauce. In my opinion it was ok but not excellent yet.\\n\\nAnyway it’s my best dim sum so far in California.\",\"languageCode\":\"en\"},\"authorAttribution\":{\"displayName\":\"Como N.\",\"uri\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/106991868919665028788/reviews\",\"photoUri\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKtJ7mbHjYDi-rhTRn1Ud0FKMrPChO_E2MT4WoN7l6QAT0FKw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3\"},\"publishTime\":\"2024-10-07T18:20:48.227122Z\"},{\"name\":\"places/ChIJZ1SMEQeBhYAR8Y0suKMr48o/reviews/ChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUM3N2RMZ1VBEAE\",\"relativePublishTimeDescription\":\"prije 2 mjeseca\",\"rating\":5,\"text\":{\"text\":\"Rezervirali smo večeru u subotu u 18:30 i drago nam je što jesmo - bilo je užurbano.\\n\\nNarudžba je iznosila oko 110 dolara za dvoje, sve uključeno - ali mislim da su kvalitetni sastojci i nepretenciozna, super pažljiva usluga vrijedni toga za posebne prilike.\\n\\nMorate nabaviti njihovu živu ribu kuhanu na pari - i jesti + umak uz rižu! Također smo naručili vegetarijansku gusku + zeleni grah (bez svinjetine), koji su bili ukusni. Kad bih se morao zajebavati, to bi bilo samo to što je jelo od zelenih mahuna bilo malo premalo za cijenu (previše nam se svidjelo).\",\"languageCode\":\"hr-HR\"},\"originalText\":{\"text\":\"We made reservations for dinner on a Sat at 6:30pm and glad we did - it was bustling.\\n\\nOrder came to be about $110 for two, all included - but i think the quality ingredients and unpretentious, super attentive service is way worth it for special occasions.\\n\\nYou have to get their live steamed fish - and have it + sauce over rice! We also ordered the vegetarian goose + green beans (no pork), which were all tasty. If I had to nitpick, it’d just be that the green beans dish was a tad small for the price (we liked it too much).\",\"languageCode\":\"en\"},\"authorAttribution\":{\"displayName\":\"Christine C\",\"uri\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/101329721628864533209/reviews\",\"photoUri\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVu_q82QLk-48Huf57jKvrmy9Gt55c21V2tl1iyWSHOW0oh3r6iqw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4\"},\"publishTime\":\"2024-08-18T04:27:16.672101Z\"},{\"name\":\"places/ChIJZ1SMEQeBhYAR8Y0suKMr48o/reviews/ChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUNMOTRlNVFnEAE\",\"relativePublishTimeDescription\":\"prije 4 mjeseca\",\"rating\":5,\"text\":{\"text\":\"Ukusna vrhunska kineska hrana gdje je sve na jelovniku bilo fantastično. Slatke BBQ svinjske lepinje bile su omiljene publici. Wontons od crvenog čili ulja bili su ukusni, ali nisu bili previše ljuti. Pola pekinške pekinške patke bilo je odlično. Široki rezanci s govedinom su ukusni, a čili mahune su bile izvrsne. Za završetak deserta morate nabaviti kolače s kremom od jaja i peciva s tekućom kremom.\",\"languageCode\":\"hr-HR\"},\"originalText\":{\"text\":\"Delicious high-end Chinese food where everything on the menu was fantastic. The sweet BBQ pork buns were a crowd favorite. The red chili oil wontons were flavorful without being too spicy. Half a Beijing Peking duck was great. The wide noodles with beef are tasty and the chili string beans were great. To wrap up dessert, the egg custard tarts and the liquid custard buns are a must-get item.\",\"languageCode\":\"en\"},\"authorAttribution\":{\"displayName\":\"Victor Wang\",\"uri\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/110371788462060280274/reviews\",\"photoUri\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU9YaKA5V6g39z0bHdV91QZTEBrhW6BNNM0Z74AsIofZjIVoTuZ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba8\"},\"publishTime\":\"2024-06-24T00:57:43.421234Z\"},{\"name\":\"places/ChIJZ1SMEQeBhYAR8Y0suKMr48o/reviews/ChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUNYcHQ3WkVnEAE\",\"relativePublishTimeDescription\":\"prije tjedan dana\",\"rating\":4,\"text\":{\"text\":\"Obavezno kada posjetite San Francisco.  Kad tamo dobiti njihov potpis jelo Singapore chili rakovica.    Nije ljut, ali je malo neuredan za jesti, ali okus je vrijedan toga.  Umak je bio odličan na riži.  Prsa i repa s juhom bili su topli i utješni.  Prsa su vrlo nježna.  Patlidžan s umakom od češnjaka bio je dobar, ali pomalo ljut.\\nObavezno napravite rezervacije jer može biti prilično prometno.\",\"languageCode\":\"hr-HR\"},\"originalText\":{\"text\":\"A must when visiting San Francisco.  When there get their signature dish Singapore chili crab.    It isn't spicy but is a bit messy to eat, but the taste is worth it.  The sauce was great on rice.  The brisket and turnip with broth was warm and comforting.  The brisket is very tender.  The eggplant with garlic sauce was good but a tad spicy.\\nMake sure to make reservations as it can get quite busy.\",\"languageCode\":\"en\"},\"authorAttribution\":{\"displayName\":\"Lorraine Pai\",\"uri\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/114060502393127063576/reviews\",\"photoUri\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVW71BgqrBNiX2JeJabccR4tT6HYpBf7L4P6xMiz082T_8AhA7x=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5\"},\"publishTime\":\"2024-10-16T01:30:15.822Z\"}],\"photos\":[{\"name\":\"places/ChIJZ1SMEQeBhYAR8Y0suKMr48o/photos/AdCG2DOeRp7JXEFZW20lLsN-vWp1oPUsjY9vmWpGkd0xDR4H5d6aWNqC_cShfcdfm4ctnFSoYHBoEKoebcn-KsV4q_JGYMWU7En3ZcRreTIhnaQqnvQ-kE3gTXQP5ZBCfmUKCOGbuWTY1lDTKczV1jFL3Ov04wOR81KWCYht\",\"widthPx\":777,\"heightPx\":684,\"authorAttributions\":[{\"displayName\":\"Harborview Restaurant & Bar\",\"uri\":\"https://maps.google.com/maps/contrib/100548883109206998367\",\"photoUri\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUdxLmL6NOOtaXmphUpyICc3Egu9na1EY-wuDx7GxibRkqBwjaZ=s100-p-k-no-mo\"}]},{\"name\":\"places/ChIJZ1SMEQeBhYAR8Y0suKMr48o/photos/AdCG2DMyz9iHGZb-qi7wO96oppFbsChAXoUvj1Iwo1yuE9uO9zRcz9fhVq4zKLOhYejNhWI7mQgdhM4dk8v5X_Wwr2Mc_pa7wX5SBxp0uvcUNaensTnaNyg4n-w93ih5fQ6xvztsDo97pGvN3KdQfRVS_I0c9mfZTw4V7R8p\",\"widthPx\":777,\"heightPx\":816,\"authorAttributions\":[{\"displayName\":\"Harborview Restaurant & Bar\",\"uri\":\"https://maps.g