":24}}},{\"open\":{\"day\":5,\"hour\":11,\"minute\":30,\"date\":{\"year\":2024,\"month\":10,\"day\":25}},\"close\":{\"day\":5,\"hour\":20,\"minute\":0,\"date\":{\"year\":2024,\"month\":10,\"day\":25}}},{\"open\":{\"day\":6,\"hour\":11,\"minute\":0,\"date\":{\"year\":2024,\"month\":10,\"day\":26}},\"close\":{\"day\":6,\"hour\":20,\"minute\":0,\"date\":{\"year\":2024,\"month\":10,\"day\":26}}}],\"weekdayDescriptions\":[\"ponedjeljak: 11:30 – 20:00\",\"utorak: 11:30 – 20:00\",\"srijeda: 11:30 – 20:00\",\"četvrtak: 11:30 – 20:00\",\"petak: 11:30 – 20:00\",\"subota: 11:00 – 20:00\",\"nedjelja: 11:00 – 20:00\"]},\"primaryType\":\"restaurant\",\"shortFormattedAddress\":\"Ferry Building, #11, San Francisco\",\"editorialSummary\":{\"text\":\"Contemporary waterside seafood eatery serving local oysters and clams, plus craft cocktails.\",\"languageCode\":\"en\"},\"reviews\":[{\"name\":\"places/ChIJWTGPjmaAhYARgXpiJ-aACYM/reviews/ChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUNYX29IdVp3EAE\",\"relativePublishTimeDescription\":\"u zadnjih tjedan dana\",\"rating\":5,\"text\":{\"text\":\"Super popularan restoran.  Morao sam malo čekati u redu da sjednem, ali red se brzo pomicao.  Hrana je općenito bila dobra i dobre vrijednosti za SF.  Najdraži su mi bili prženi inćuni.  Sve je stiglo super brzo i osoblje je bilo pažljivo.\",\"languageCode\":\"hr-HR\"},\"originalText\":{\"text\":\"Super popular restaurant.  Had to wait a bit in line to get seated but line moved fast.  Food overall was good and of good value for SF.  My favorite was the fried anchovies.  Everything came out super fast and wait staff was attentive.\",\"languageCode\":\"en\"},\"authorAttribution\":{\"displayName\":\"Qin Zhu\",\"uri\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/105369061636306912298/reviews\",\"photoUri\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVAT-kvZC4PrMRGa9_sGuJcyMdatOddLtIZ1mgM7-Nkk9YPfq4K=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4\"},\"publishTime\":\"2024-10-17T05:54:36.958590Z\"},{\"name\":\"places/ChIJWTGPjmaAhYARgXpiJ-aACYM/reviews/ChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSURIaTRTM0xBEAE\",\"relativePublishTimeDescription\":\"prije mjesec dana\",\"rating\":5,\"text\":{\"text\":\"Imao sam najčudesniji solo ručak u Hog Island Oyster Co. u San Franciscu. Njihove dagnje, prožete afričkim okusima, bile su bez sumnje najbolje koje sam ikada probao. U kombinaciji sa savršenom čašom bijelog vina, i sve to uz pogled na mirne vode - bio je to nezaboravan podnevni bijeg. Okruženje je bilo savršeno za lagani predah prije nastavka opuštene šetnje rivom. Topla preporuka svima koji traže ukusnu morsku hranu i slikovito, opušteno iskustvo!\\n\\nPS Ovo je bio moj drugi posjet ovom putovanju\\n\U0001fa75🌊⛅️😉\",\"languageCode\":\"hr-HR\"},\"originalText\":{\"text\":\"I had the most amazing solo lunch at Hog Island Oyster Co. in San Francisco. Their mussels, infused with African flavors, were hands down the best I’ve ever tasted. Paired with the perfect glass of white wine, and all while overlooking the serene waters—it was an unforgettable midday escape. The setting was perfect for a leisurely break before continuing on a relaxed stroll along the waterfront. Highly recommend for anyone looking for delicious seafood and a scenic, laid-back experience!\\n\\nPS This was my second visit here this trip\\n\U0001fa75🌊⛅️😉\",\"languageCode\":\"en\"},\"authorAttribution\":{\"displayName\":\"Jerica Saddler Bragner\",\"uri\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/107060331907193519012/reviews\",\"photoUri\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVNWMQt-JiP_FiVIfHcEkcq0urhhdj9jRE-dYN7Y1YKNfN7Rx4ZLw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba2\"},\"publishTime\":\"2024-09-19T21:06:24.834570Z\"},{\"name\":\"places/ChIJWTGPjmaAhYARgXpiJ-aACYM/reviews/ChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUM3X3VhQmp3RRAB\",\"relativePublishTimeDescription\":\"prije 2 mjeseca\",\"rating\":5,\"text\":{\"text\":\"Sve što sam želio za rođendan ove godine bile su kamenice. Moj rođak je predložio ovaj restoran za moj rođendanski ručak, znajući da sam veliki ljubitelj kamenica. Ovo je prošlo kao jedan od najboljih rođendanskih ručkova koje sam ikada imao. Počeo sam sa slanim kolačem od kamenica, koji je bio vrlo ukusan i zadovoljavajući. Iako obično pijem slatke i/ili voćne napitke, ovaj slani napitak je pokazao moje okusne pupoljke. Tih 6 kamenica koje sam naručio bile su stvarno fenomenalne. Svaki je imao jedinstven i osvježavajući okus. Ničije iznenađenje, pojeo sam kamenice. Na kraju, rustikalni gulaš od morskih plodova bio je savršeno jelo. Od svih variva s plodovima mora koje sam probala, ovo je najbolje. Prštao je od okusa i nisam se mogla zasititi. Bilo je vrlo svježe, kvalitetno i savršeno u svakom pogledu. Ovaj restoran spada među moje omiljene plodove mora, posebno kamenice. Apsolutno, definitivno, visoko preporučujem.\",\"languageCode\":\"hr-HR\"},\"originalText\":{\"text\":\"All I wanted for my birthday this year was oysters. My cousin suggested this restaurant for my birthday lunch, knowing that I’m a hardcore lover of oysters. This has gone down as one of the best birthday lunches I’ve ever had. I started off with the savory oyster shooter, which was very tasty and satisfying. Although I typically get sweet and/or fruity drinks, this savory drink showed my tastebuds a great time. The 6 oysters that I ordered were truly phenomenal. Each one had a unique and refreshing taste. To no one’s surprise, I devoured the oysters. Finally, the rustic seafood stew was THE perfect dish. Out of all the seafood stews I have tried, this one tops them all. It was bursting with flavor and I couldn’t get enough. It was very fresh, high quality, and perfect in every way. This restaurant goes down as one of my top favorites for seafood, specifically oysters. I absolutely, most definitely, highly recommend.\",\"languageCode\":\"en\"},\"authorAttribution\":{\"displayName\":\"Raha Mehrkish\",\"uri\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/117705569567738867855/reviews\",\"photoUri\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUPamkweyQHUUCaqKMZaAis8uR9V53UyCLpLu5Yc5wEduBuOji4uQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4\"},\"publishTime\":\"2024-08-16T06:17:27.178320Z\"},{\"name\":\"places/ChIJWTGPjmaAhYARgXpiJ-aACYM/reviews/ChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSURIb1p1Vkx3EAE\",\"relativePublishTimeDescription\":\"prije mjesec dana\",\"rating\":5,\"text\":{\"text\":\"Posjetili smo ga početkom lipnja. Moj je suprug dolazio ovamo godinama prije i rekao da ima najbolju morsku hranu, pa smo se potrudili doći. Bilo je 100% ukusno. Volim pogled dok sjedim vani i skoro sam polizao tanjur 🍽️😋\\nSamo bih volio da postoji bolji toalet, ovako prometan kao ovo mjesto.\",\"languageCode\":\"hr-HR\"},\"originalText\":{\"text\":\"Visited here in early June. My husband had come here years before and said he had the best seafood so we made it a point to come. It 100% was delicious. Love the view when sitting outside and almost licked my plate 🍽️😋\\nOnly wish there were better restroom as busy as this place gets.\",\"languageCode\":\"en\"},\"authorAttribution\":{\"displayName\":\"Monica M.\",\"uri\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/111663964092574673330/reviews\",\"photoUri\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVtWNgIAx3Ak8fTE6UVv5P071A_h1uR_CjBXVFi98jgpOeAsJ8B=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5\"},\"publishTime\":\"2024-09-16T20:52:06.529409Z\"},{\"name\":\"places/ChIJWTGPjmaAhYARgXpiJ-aACYM/reviews/ChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUQ3NjRpM013EAE\",\"relativePublishTimeDescription\":\"prije mjesec dana\",\"rating\":5,\"text\":{\"text\":\"Kad sam stigao tamo, red je bio obeshrabrujući, ali bili su na redu i posjeli su nas za manje od 10 minuta. Prije nisam volio kamenice i nisam baš obožavatelj, ali ono što su tamo imali bilo je dobro i tako svježe. Juha od školjki i kokteli također su bili jako dobri. Pržena geoduck bila je razočaravajuća. Samo je nedostajalo okusa. Osoblje je bilo lijepo i vrlo pažljivo. Restoran je bio mali, ali su dobro iskoristili prostor i bio je vrlo čist.\",\"languageCode\":\"hr-HR\"},\"originalText\":{\"text\":\"When I got there the line was discouraging but they were on it and sat us in less than 10 minutes. I use to not like oysters and not really a fan but what they had there was good and so fresh. The clam chowder and cocktails were also really good. The fried geoduck was disappointing. Just lacked any flavor. Staff was nice and very attentive. The restaurant was small but they used the space well and was very clean.\",\"languageCode\":\"en\"},\"authorAttribution\":{\"displayName\":\"Oscar\",\"uri\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/103244058329014498611/reviews\",\"photoUri\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUTYtW50JYertdxLUmANTckQZmOt39fTohT08CihvGU9VMkVvyNAA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5\"},\"publishTime\":\"2024-08-28T16:59:26.288850Z\"}],\"photos\":[{\"name\":\"places/ChIJWTGPjmaAhYARgXpiJ-aACYM/photos/AdCG2DMC_mWhXXA8IGjymqTbMllIaynd_ZfYty4ESMgKJayz_9C8rqTYN0EzI2eOlfjtBHe4yjnBAXGNwAWe9bcDRRgKiOONr6RaJj8ycIN73e5cHrrKHfNb0zN_4Kws7enXn4RXMOjyacAFHNdvbGfRuMgB4JjDoi1IfTTL\",\"widthPx\":4800,\"heightPx\":3120,\"authorAttributions\":[{\"displayName\":\"Hog Island Oyster Co.\",\"uri\":\"https://maps.google.com/maps/contrib/111592707657525468627\",\"photoUri\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX6rRI9Nw_7_0LqJM9I39LlMYLpk0MhaB4jZKXUFnpLT28rrcI=s100-p-k-no-mo\"}]},{\"name\":\"places/ChIJWTGPjmaAhYARgXpiJ-aACYM/photos/AdCG2DOgNllBMgelaGYEnhiQ2nIrZsuTIbvsdascrQOpJ3wECnX2SWRfcfIEtb2iYe-dx3MRuBqe0soL9G21MQ9J6pqOC3_uh_WfgPsXMcdmaAejJ5TXVWAcjC-U7oerbnJkPsw3gfuSlRW0WBQbR_QItFu17lPE4idIPwvX\",\"widthPx\":2400,\"heightPx\":3600,\"authorAttributions\":[{\"displayName\":\"Hog Island Oyster Co.\",\"uri\":\"https://maps.google.com/maps/contrib/111592707657525468627\",\"photoUri\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX6rRI9Nw_7_0LqJM9I39LlMYLpk0MhaB4jZKXUFnpLT28rrcI=s100-p-k-no-mo\"}]},{\"name\":\"places/ChIJWTGPjmaAhYARgXpiJ-aACYM/photos/AdCG2DM4rjvCS4P3NfIdSPabGtLWdl1LQ0Xdsya8wyB7C0zeFjG0FGoGXM37x6AEtZgbutAndSH9fxReXDHw0kicALPVfrJW4s3hjNP5YQIiSgA6jOVJ7cAOguIze0DTqPydU_2KdSTaO6G049NXUsg45rkOTxG