"hour\":14,\"minute\":30,\"date\":{\"year\":2024,\"month\":10,\"day\":23}}},{\"open\":{\"day\":3,\"hour\":16,\"minute\":30,\"date\":{\"year\":2024,\"month\":10,\"day\":23}},\"close\":{\"day\":3,\"hour\":21,\"minute\":30,\"date\":{\"year\":2024,\"month\":10,\"day\":23}}},{\"open\":{\"day\":4,\"hour\":11,\"minute\":0,\"date\":{\"year\":2024,\"month\":10,\"day\":24}},\"close\":{\"day\":4,\"hour\":14,\"minute\":30,\"date\":{\"year\":2024,\"month\":10,\"day\":24}}},{\"open\":{\"day\":4,\"hour\":16,\"minute\":30,\"date\":{\"year\":2024,\"month\":10,\"day\":24}},\"close\":{\"day\":4,\"hour\":21,\"minute\":30,\"date\":{\"year\":2024,\"month\":10,\"day\":24}}},{\"open\":{\"day\":5,\"hour\":11,\"minute\":0,\"date\":{\"year\":2024,\"month\":10,\"day\":25}},\"close\":{\"day\":5,\"hour\":14,\"minute\":30,\"date\":{\"year\":2024,\"month\":10,\"day\":25}}},{\"open\":{\"day\":5,\"hour\":16,\"minute\":30,\"date\":{\"year\":2024,\"month\":10,\"day\":25}},\"close\":{\"day\":5,\"hour\":21,\"minute\":30,\"date\":{\"year\":2024,\"month\":10,\"day\":25}}},{\"open\":{\"day\":6,\"hour\":16,\"minute\":30,\"date\":{\"year\":2024,\"month\":10,\"day\":26}},\"close\":{\"day\":6,\"hour\":21,\"minute\":30,\"date\":{\"year\":2024,\"month\":10,\"day\":26}}}],\"weekdayDescriptions\":[\"ponedjeljak: 11:00 – 14:30, 16:30 – 21:30\",\"utorak: 11:00 – 14:30, 16:30 – 21:30\",\"srijeda: 11:00 – 14:30, 16:30 – 21:30\",\"četvrtak: 11:00 – 14:30, 16:30 – 21:30\",\"petak: 11:00 – 14:30, 16:30 – 21:30\",\"subota: 16:30 – 21:30\",\"nedjelja: Zatvoreno\"]},\"primaryType\":\"seafood_restaurant\",\"shortFormattedAddress\":\"240 California St, San Francisco\",\"editorialSummary\":{\"text\":\"Institution for fresh fish and classic cocktails with an old-school setting and a lively atmosphere.\",\"languageCode\":\"en\"},\"reviews\":[{\"name\":\"places/ChIJqVjXkGGAhYAR5X80yCKz9Wo/reviews/ChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUNIcmZudlBREAE\",\"relativePublishTimeDescription\":\"prije mjesec dana\",\"rating\":3,\"text\":{\"text\":\"Usluga je izuzetna, isplati se doći samo zbog toga. Vratio bih se po piće i predjelo, ali vjerojatno više ne bih imao punu večeru. Kolač od rakova bio je ukusan i ne štede na rakovima, brancin je bio dobar, ali ne i odličan, a biftek je bio pečen na roštilju, nije imao okus kao dobar komad mesa. Sve je povrće bilo bljutavo.\",\"languageCode\":\"hr-HR\"},\"originalText\":{\"text\":\"Service is exceptional, worth coming just for that. I would come back for drinks and an appetizer but probably wouldn’t have a full dinner again. Crab cake was delicious and they don’t skimp on the crab, sea bass was good but not great, and steak was hammered on the grill, didn’t taste like a good piece of meat. Veggies were all bland.\",\"languageCode\":\"en\"},\"authorAttribution\":{\"displayName\":\"Jack Brown\",\"uri\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/111000318534300148240/reviews\",\"photoUri\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIDxOjs-mwIA20er3s3YkI6hYHFUJsBbeI_nYyA0z6xjgS90A=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5\"},\"publishTime\":\"2024-09-07T16:59:52.586170Z\"},{\"name\":\"places/ChIJqVjXkGGAhYAR5X80yCKz9Wo/reviews/ChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUM3alBpWmJnEAE\",\"relativePublishTimeDescription\":\"prije 2 mjeseca\",\"rating\":5,\"text\":{\"text\":\"Mjesto je dragulj, možete udahnuti povijest i tradiciju. Osoblje je bilo pristojno i ljubazno, kao i vrlo pažljivo u pružanju usluga. Jelovnik na kojem prevladava riba, naručujemo također vodeći se savjetima konobara i uživamo u zaista super večeri. Hvala vam puno, vidimo se uskoro! 🙏🏻\",\"languageCode\":\"hr-HR\"},\"originalText\":{\"text\":\"Il locale è una chicca, si respirano storia e tradizione. Il personale gentile e cordiale, oltre che molto attento nel servizio. Menù con una dominanza di pesce, ordiniamo facendoci guidare anche dai consigli del cameriere, e ci godiamo una cena davvero super. Grazie mille, a presto! 🙏🏻\",\"languageCode\":\"it\"},\"authorAttribution\":{\"displayName\":\"Giorgio Riva\",\"uri\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/109895842543008055487/reviews\",\"photoUri\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUX5IA0tltM0hqXV5Lxdr4SB0JvRzC6kQ2Lf7nxqF7atXkCHJDMtg=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5\"},\"publishTime\":\"2024-08-13T05:42:00.969193Z\"},{\"name\":\"places/ChIJqVjXkGGAhYAR5X80yCKz9Wo/reviews/ChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUM3dmVxSVNREAE\",\"relativePublishTimeDescription\":\"prije 2 mjeseca\",\"rating\":3,\"text\":{\"text\":\"Nedavno sam večerao u Tadich Grillu i sveukupno je to bilo prosječno iskustvo. Hrana je bila pristojna, ali ne i izuzetna. Besplatan kruh poslužen na početku bio je hladan, a ne topao, što je bilo pomalo razočaravajuće. Njihov popularni cioppino s morskim plodovima, kojem sam se radovao, nije imao jarku crvenu boju zrelih rajčica, što ga je činilo manje privlačnim. Atmosfera je bila dovoljno ugodna, a usluga u redu, iako se ništa nije isticalo. To je dobro mjesto, ali ima boljih opcija u gradu.\",\"languageCode\":\"hr-HR\"},\"originalText\":{\"text\":\"I recently dined at Tadich Grill, and it was an average experience overall. The food was decent, but not exceptional. The free bread served at the beginning was cold rather than warm, which was a bit disappointing. Their popular seafood cioppino, which I was looking forward to, lacked the vibrant red color of ripe tomatoes, making it less visually appealing. The atmosphere was pleasant enough, and the service was fine, though nothing stood out. It's an okay spot, but there are better options in town.\",\"languageCode\":\"en\"},\"authorAttribution\":{\"displayName\":\"Nguyet Le\",\"uri\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/100413160453721837256/reviews\",\"photoUri\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVS_xahnxzsM7TLc7efdzdfBwYMDOVy23CHHgOu_Qe80FNmk15jtg=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba2\"},\"publishTime\":\"2024-08-18T10:23:52.451016Z\"},{\"name\":\"places/ChIJqVjXkGGAhYAR5X80yCKz9Wo/reviews/ChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUNuNnRmTWxRRRAB\",\"relativePublishTimeDescription\":\"prije 4 tjedna\",\"rating\":4,\"text\":{\"text\":\"Pregled ručka\\nJa sam jeo odrezak s lignjama. Vrlo dobro. Volio sam krumpire i tikvice.  Rak/kozica a la Monza je bio ok. Velike kozice, ali bez okusa.\\nNajnegativnija je bila buka. NIJE mirno okruženje.\\nSjajno je doživjeti ikonu SF-a, ali kao i neki drugi restorani koji su ikone, ovo je bilo bučno. Ali vrijedi ga posjetiti kako biste doživjeli klasičan SF trenutak.\",\"languageCode\":\"hr-HR\"},\"originalText\":{\"text\":\"Lunch review\\nI had the calamari steak. Very good. Loved the potatoes and squash.  The crab/prawn a la Monza was ok. Large prawns but it lacked flavor.\\nMost negative was the noise. It is NOT a quiet environment.\\nGreat to experience a SF icon, but like some of the other eateries that are icons, this was noisy. But worth a visit to experience a classic SF time.\",\"languageCode\":\"en\"},\"authorAttribution\":{\"displayName\":\"Russ Lewis\",\"uri\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/103209757896548505068/reviews\",\"photoUri\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKFjMkeLt63lEIgkfdlEXpZ2NRjjSqr7JkymUQjY20FO7Y-cw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5\"},\"publishTime\":\"2024-09-25T02:40:27.886299Z\"},{\"name\":\"places/ChIJqVjXkGGAhYAR5X80yCKz9Wo/reviews/ChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSURyNkttdmZBEAE\",\"relativePublishTimeDescription\":\"prije 3 mjeseca\",\"rating\":3,\"text\":{\"text\":\"Nevjerojatna atmosfera i usluga. Šef kuće bio je nevjerojatan ambasador restorana. Obroci su bili uspješni. 2 goveđa odreska su bila plava, za razliku od srednje pečena, ravioli su bili ok, a ciopino izvrstan.\",\"languageCode\":\"hr-HR\"},\"originalText\":{\"text\":\"Amazing atmosphere and service. Head of house was an incredible ambassador for the restaurant. Meals were hit and miss. 2 beef tenderloin steaks were blue rare as opposed to medium rare, ravioli was ok and ciopino was excellent.\",\"languageCode\":\"en\"},\"authorAttribution\":{\"displayName\":\"James Bond\",\"uri\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/111086426963049979336/reviews\",\