for Mediterranean cuisine. I've walked by it numerous times and was finally able to visit. The food and service were excellent. The atmosphere was warm and inviting. Everything appeared clean and well-maintained. I would definitely return.\",\"languageCode\":\"en\"},\"authorAttribution\":{\"displayName\":\"Sayana\",\"uri\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/104417721466509391942/reviews\",\"photoUri\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKHts-VO9JOmetFcbfANWasnCA9CF1mhw-jF9XKa8OuIGDl9g=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5\"},\"publishTime\":\"2024-09-11T00:02:15.299993Z\"},{\"name\":\"places/ChIJDzBboWOAhYARKT5j0sGvFDU/reviews/ChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUNudzdqR1ZBEAE\",\"relativePublishTimeDescription\":\"prije 3 tjedna\",\"rating\":5,\"text\":{\"text\":\"Barcha SF nudi živopisno gastronomsko iskustvo sa svojim jelovnikom nadahnutim Mediteranom, koji sadrži svježa, aromatična jela koja će vas odvesti na obalu. Otmjeni ambijent, ljubazno osoblje i izvrsni kokteli čine ga savršenim za večernji spoj ili grupno okupljanje.\",\"languageCode\":\"hr-HR\"},\"originalText\":{\"text\":\"Barcha SF offers a vibrant dining experience with its Mediterranean-inspired menu, featuring fresh, flavorful dishes that transport you to the coast. The chic ambiance, friendly staff, and great cocktails make it perfect for a date night or group gathering.\",\"languageCode\":\"en\"},\"authorAttribution\":{\"displayName\":\"Vash\",\"uri\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/111600509426744294569/reviews\",\"photoUri\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVlBjCO6gkA1mhk1zVBDzfmyLpX3YyurlMdnpEucy8svW-aFRUh=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6\"},\"publishTime\":\"2024-09-29T06:20:55.478461Z\"},{\"name\":\"places/ChIJDzBboWOAhYARKT5j0sGvFDU/reviews/ChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSURyMzlhRlhBEAE\",\"relativePublishTimeDescription\":\"prije 3 mjeseca\",\"rating\":5,\"text\":{\"text\":\"Odabrali smo Barchu za proslavu naše obljetnice. Na kraju smo uživali samo u njihovim predjelima jer ih je bilo previše za odabir. Janjeće pure i Janjeće kofte su najbolje. Dobili smo izvrsnu uslugu od našeg domaćina, kao i konobara i kuhara koji su nam sami poslužili nekoliko jela i poželjeli nam. Osigurali su nam i dodatni desert i bio je fantastičan. Topla preporuka da uzmete desert baklavu.\",\"languageCode\":\"hr-HR\"},\"originalText\":{\"text\":\"We chose Barcha to celebrate our anniversary. We ended up enjoying only their appetisers because the were just too many to choose from. Lamb cigars and Lamb Kofte are the best. We got wonderful service from our host as well as the waiter and the chef made it a point to serve us a couple dishes himself and wished us. They also provided a complementary dessert for us and it was fantastic. Highly recommend getting the baklava dessert.\",\"languageCode\":\"en\"},\"authorAttribution\":{\"displayName\":\"Bhishman Desai\",\"uri\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/108715502754393934815/reviews\",\"photoUri\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVyz4TsnwhmFlLQZ-BzZHCRunLgBcCrUhI51wSZUeXr_GF7roZT=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba2\"},\"publishTime\":\"2024-07-21T17:49:06.466854Z\"},{\"name\":\"places/ChIJDzBboWOAhYARKT5j0sGvFDU/reviews/ChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUNuOTlyTUZ3EAE\",\"relativePublishTimeDescription\":\"prije 3 tjedna\",\"rating\":5,\"text\":{\"text\":\"Bio sam ovdje dva puta i apsolutno mi se sviđa! Hrana je pomalo masna po mom ukusu, ali je tako ukusna, a baklava je nevjerojatna! Definitivno must have. Pokušao sam:\\nVeganska janjeća kofta- fantastična\\nHrskavi falafel - pomalo suh ali to je problem falafela\\nHumus - nevjerojatan!\\nShakshuka - super\\nFalafel omot - također je jako dobar\\nBaklava- NEVJEROJATNAGGG\",\"languageCode\":\"hr-HR\"},\"originalText\":{\"text\":\"Have been here twice and absolutely love it! The food is a bit oily for my preference but its so flavourful and the baklava is amazing! Definitely must have. I have tried:\\nVegan lamb kofta- amazing\\nCrispy falafel- a bit dry but thats falafel's problem\\nHummus- amazing!\\nShakshuka - great\\nFalafel wrap- really good as well\\nBaklava- AMAZINGGGG\",\"languageCode\":\"en\"},\"authorAttribution\":{\"displayName\":\"Akshita Gupta\",\"uri\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/112069676090025051917/reviews\",\"photoUri\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLnEj4iD_8rlu6vD8yDESzhU0r4fxDFQhfmGp_sRe6u6DMaIA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3\"},\"publishTime\":\"2024-10-01T05:27:46.940614Z\"},{\"name\":\"places/ChIJDzBboWOAhYARKT5j0sGvFDU/reviews/ChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSURUNmEzUWRREAE\",\"relativePublishTimeDescription\":\"prije 5 mj.\",\"rating\":5,\"text\":{\"text\":\"Svidjelo nam se sve što smo imali u Barchi (shakshuka, tahdig i pileći kebab). Čini se da restoran povremeno prilagođava jelovnik. Poslužitelj je bio pažljiv, pristojan i držao je naše čaše pune vode.\",\"languageCode\":\"hr-HR\"},\"originalText\":{\"text\":\"We loved everything we had at Barcha (shakshuka, tahdig, and chicken kebab). It seems like the restaurant adjusts menu occasionally. The server was observant, polite, and kept our glasses full of water.\",\"languageCode\":\"en\"},\"authorAttribution\":{\"displayName\":\"Nanase Niikura\",\"uri\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/103241416893697933496/reviews\",\"photoUri\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX5TaZ4IQShPJiE7ki4gv9X-JOqhmwjiUe3AbSA89x30b6cmmHC=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba2\"},\"publishTime\":\"2024-05-25T21:43:31.638632Z\"}],\"photos\":[{\"name\":\"places/ChIJDzBboWOAhYARKT5j0sGvFDU/photos/AdCG2DO8ZN7Ezt0ouqynVksvfIakEO3ktKqAptfBe-_jqjHvrmyrsDkC0E_6P9Q9L5Sj59mbmPyNnsbe4SbCr9M2Jb4i3jys9yfbgxH8mLdilpEZ2pfh3fSg2UhhVJDTkvlb-353uQ5kfvvhPQSK6bT6cPQhhVMiaRTtdaey\",\"widthPx\":500,\"heightPx\":375,\"authorAttributions\":[{\"displayName\":\"Barcha Restaurant\",\"uri\":\"https://maps.google.com/maps/contrib/105400563653378379499\",\"photoUri\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUbeSNnGIDllaIInMppWlW9Bh9RUVP5jodVzqh4r3Cd3hXw8Dxb=s100-p-k-no-mo\"}]},{\"name\":\"places/ChIJDzBboWOAh