googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXXz1lHNpdU2MsiNMkf3mMJ2MdfyCSrA4QZPu0eiEYGZFA8QqPE=s100-p-k-no-mo\"}]},{\"name\":\"places/ChIJDzBboWOAhYARKT5j0sGvFDU/photos/AdCG2DMiqthyrLskQAt_hU9VIPOMKlhBY347svjXeYjyjv9z02-OJs9PAzW4lNt7e1kAvI8ehKOTc7iSo-n8HXApTHKNsoCx1-Q8NrEdjlgjZ0Yp4EIRQlOXeKpa6skOOZu5k-is_9dseayBkEGIS0HqrwInPyuKC_HuBfeY\",\"widthPx\":4080,\"heightPx\":3072,\"authorAttributions\":[{\"displayName\":\"Gauri Gadkari\",\"uri\":\"https://maps.google.com/maps/contrib/102117105939783820515\",\"photoUri\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXoR3kFYsjZxzieCSooq6aROkSBANOn9XeoISryEIemeTgr2_12BA=s100-p-k-no-mo\"}]}],\"outdoorSeating\":true,\"liveMusic\":false,\"menuForChildren\":false,\"servesCocktails\":true,\"servesDessert\":true,\"servesCoffee\":true,\"goodForChildren\":false,\"allowsDogs\":false,\"restroom\":true,\"goodForGroups\":true,\"goodForWatchingSports\":false,\"paymentOptions\":{\"acceptsCreditCards\":true,\"acceptsDebitCards\":false,\"acceptsCashOnly\":false,\"acceptsNfc\":true},\"accessibilityOptions\":{\"wheelchairAccessibleParking\":true,\"wheelchairAccessibleEntrance\":true,\"wheelchairAccessibleRestroom\":true,\"wheelchairAccessibleSeating\":true},\"generativeSummary\":{\"overview\":{\"text\":\"Mediterranean restaurant offering a selection of small plates and entrees, plus cocktails and wine.\",\"languageCode\":\"en-US\"},\"description\":{\"text\":\"Upscale Mediterranean restaurant in the Financial District with a bar, outdoor patio, and happy hour.\\nThe menu features dishes from Southern France, Spain, Tunisia, and the Middle East. People recommend the lamb, falafel, and barcha spreads, as well as the drinks.\\nGuests praise the ambiance and attentive staff. Reservations are recommended.\\nCustomers typically spend $50–100.\",\"languageCode\":\"en-US\"},\"references\":{\"reviews\":[{\"name\":\"places/ChIJDzBboWOAhYARKT5j0sGvFDU/reviews/ChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUN4OUs3RVl3EAE\",\"relativePublishTimeDescription\":\"prije godinu dana\",\"rating\":5,\"text\":{\"text\":\"Wow! Kakav sladak restoran. Moj muž je to pronašao na Googleu kada je tražio \\\"rođendanski romantični restorani za ženu\\\". I pobijedio je!\\nAmbijent je savršen. Ima i vani i unutra. Grijalice vani za hladne sf večeri ili jutra.\\nUkusna pića. Dobra hrana. Super uslužni konobari i odlična usluga.\\nMi smo vegetarijanci i pomogli su nam u nabavi dobre hrane i prilagodbi.\",\"languageCode\":\"hr-HR\"},\"originalText\":{\"text\":\"Wow! What a cute restaurant. My husband found this on google when he searched for “birthday romantic restaurants for wife”. And he won!\\nThe ambiance is perfect. There’s outside seating and inside too. Heaters outside for cold sf evenings or mornings.\\nDelicious drinks. Good food. Super helpful waiters and excellent service.\\nWe are vegetarian and they helped us out with getting good food and customizations.\",\"languageCode\":\"en\"},\"authorAttribution\":{\"displayName\":\"Shilpa M\",\"uri\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/109947967262088214629/reviews\",\"photoUri\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX1PzRcHVqIf2EwhhxiDA265_4wYvmHEtaTkTXdNdDDM6xxOw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4\"},\"publishTime\":\"2023-05-11T19:04:35.395642Z\"},{\"name\":\"places/ChIJDzBboWOAhYARKT5j0sGvFDU/reviews/ChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUNZcXRXS0V3EAE\",\"relativePublishTimeDescription\":\"prije godinu dana\",\"rating\":5,\"text\":{\"text\":\"Vrlo ukusna hrana. Ljubazno osoblje. Bilo je jako zaposleno u vrijeme ručka, pa smo morali sjediti za šankom, ali to također znači da nema čekanja. Dakle, tu se nema što žaliti. Sve u svemu, vrlo dobro iskustvo. Definitivno ću se vratiti tamo.\\n\\nAžurirati:\\nDanas sam ponovno posjetio ovo mjesto prvi put nakon pandemije COVID-a. I nisu razočarali. Izvrsna hrana i piće. Ako ste ovdje, morate probati ćevap od janjećeg kefta! To je rajski!\",\"languageCode\":\"hr-HR\"},\"originalText\":{\"text\":\"Very tasty food. Courteous staff. Was very busy at lunch time, so we had to sit at the bar, but that also meant no wait. So nothing to complain there. Overall, a very good experience. Will definitely go back there.\\n\\nUpdate:\\nVisited this place again for the first time after the COVID pandemic today. And they didn't disappoint. Amazing food and drinks. If you're here, you have to try the Lamb Kefta kebab! It's heavenly!\",\"languageCode\":\"en\"},\"authorAttribution\":{\"displayName\":\"Gurjinder Singh Rathore\",\"uri\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/104662436811329379919/reviews\",\"photoUri\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXCDs_4VkWxdyR3W0NAqnb6tQNdVXDR80qRCS3e5socrJaDt-_h1Q=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4\"},\"publishTime\":\"2023-07-22T02:55:27.210621Z\"},{\"name\":\"places/ChIJDzBboWOAhYARKT5j0sGvFDU/reviews/ChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUN4eXNDM2xnRRAB\",\"relativePublishTimeDescription\":\"prije godinu dana\",\"rating\":5,\"text\":{\"text\":\"Tako sjajno iskustvo ovdje! Svaki član osoblja s kojim smo komunicirali bio je tako ljubazan i od pomoći. Podijelili smo nekoliko mezze tanjura. Salata od šparoga s burratom bila je nevjerojatna, a janjetina Kosta bila je izvrsna. Svakako uzmite Barcha namaze. Zanimalo nas je što se nalazi u jednom jelu, a kuhar je došao i sve nam s oduševljenjem objasnio. Također nam je rekao za još jedno jelo koje nismo naručili (okruglice), ali bilo je omiljeno publici. Zatim nam je donio dvije knedle da probamo! Poslužitelji su čuli da mi je rođendan pa su na kraju večeri donijeli komad torte. Sam restoran je prekrasan, a usluga izvrsna. Visoko preporučeno!\",\"languageCode\":\"hr-HR\"},\"originalText\":{\"text\":\"Such a great experience here! Every single staff member we interacted with were so kind and helpful. We shared a number of the mezze plates. The asparagus salad with burrata was amazing and the lamb Kosta was delicious. Definitely get the Barcha spreads. We were curious about what was in one dish and the chef came over and explained everything with enthusiasm. He also told us about another dish we didn't order (the dumplings), but was a crowd favorite. Then he brought us over two dumplings to try! The servers heard it was my birthday so they brought over a piece of cake at the end of the night. The restaurant itself is beautiful and the service was excellent. Highly recommend!\",\"languageCode\":\"en\"},\"authorAttribution\":{\"displayName\":\"rebekka schnitter\",\"uri\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/110856384598592752041/reviews\",\"photoUri\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIlCQqNpIKgN3IfUEXNJYnPtTtfc2HjYeqYl9S2f-lVcl5OXw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo\"},\"publishTime\":\"2023-05-15T00:27:01.627864Z\"},{\"name\":\"places/ChIJDzBboWOAhYARKT5j0sGvFDU/reviews/ChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUNKNG96bXp3RRAB\",\"relativePublishTimeDescription\":\"prije godinu dana\",\"rating\":5,\"text\":{\"text\":\"Otišao sam u Barchu u posljednji trenutak kako bih proslavio svoj 28. rođendan, moram reći da su Kais, Kosta i njihovo besprijekorno osoblje dali sve od sebe da me ugoste u posljednjem trenutku. U restoranu vlada takva atmosfera, a ambijent je izvrstan. Ako nikada niste bili u Sjevernoj Africi, Kais i njegovo osoblje unijet će okus Sjeverne Afrike u vašu paletu. Osjećat ćete se kao da ste osobno tamo. 10/10, sigurno ću opet posjetiti i dovesti prijatelje. 🙏🏾\",\"languageCode\":\"hr-HR\"},\"originalText\":{\"text\":\"I went to Barcha at the last minute to celebrate my 28th birthday I must say Kais,  Kosta, and their impeccable staff went above and beyond to accommodate me at the last minute. The restaurant is such a vibe and the ambience is superb. If you’ve never been to North Africa, Kais and his staff will bring the taste of North Africa to your palette. You’ll feel like you’re there in person. 10/10, I will definitely visit again and bring friends. 🙏🏾\",\"languageCode\":\"en\"},\"authorAttribution\":{\"displayName\":\"Naeem Chism\",\"uri\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/113635473390634532722/reviews\",\"photoUri\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVXwwsL-jqZT83pVqsw4Uz5TYFM4l9Autyjbxw-aTEl2g-ZDpCr0g=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo\"},\"publishTime\":\"2023-06-23T19:53:16.861405Z\"},{\"name\":\"places/ChIJDzBboWOAhYARKT5j0sGvFDU/reviews/ChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSURKaHBfZHBBRRAB\",\"relativePublishTimeDescription\":\"prije godinu dana\",\"rating\":5,\"text\":{\"text\":\"Dobar izbor za izvrsnu mediteransku hranu. Imaju sjedenje u zatvorenom prostoru i terasu na otvorenom. Barcha namaz je bio dobar, ali morate platiti dodatni kruh, a na stolu nemaju bocu maslinovog ulja. Falafel je bio remek-djelo. Vegetarijanska ponuda je ograničena, ali spremni su prilagoditi jela za vas. Mogao sam vidjeti brojne ljude kako uživaju u ćevapima. Svidio mi se starinski koktel i usluga je bila jednostavno vrhunska. Kamal je poznavao jelovnik i znao je dobro objasniti jela te nam je pomogao pri odabiru. Malo skupo, ali u skladu s vrhunskom lokacijom. Vrijedno iskustva.\",\"languageCode\":\"hr-HR\"},\"originalText\":{\"text\":\"A good choice for some excellent Mediterranean food. They have indoor seating and an Outdoor Patio. The Barcha Spread was nice but you need to pay for extra bread and they don’t have an Olive oil bottle on the table. The Falafel was a masterpiece. The Vegetarian spread is limited but they are open to tweak dishes for you. I could see a number of people enjoying the Kebabs. Loved the Old Fashioned Cocktail and the service was just superb. Kamal knew the menu and could explain the dishes well and helped us select. A little expensive but in line with the premium location. Worth the experience .\",\"languageCode\":\"en\"},\"authorAttribution\":{\"displayName\":\"Sachidanand Madan\",\"uri\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/103981466114292221332/reviews\",\"photoUri\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVjbwQdShgEVyX5Plq27o9MYlHxli4JYBpigOVfeIuqOHEnSsg=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5\"},\"publishTime\":\"2023-07-15T20:25:21.940891Z\"}]}},\"addressDescriptor\":{\"landmarks\":[{\"name\":\"places/ChIJ1dIqa2OAhYAREimtEt