\":2024,\"month\":10,\"day\":25}}},{\"open\":{\"day\":6,\"hour\":16,\"minute\":0,\"date\":{\"year\":2024,\"month\":10,\"day\":26}},\"close\":{\"day\":6,\"hour\":22,\"minute\":0,\"date\":{\"year\":2024,\"month\":10,\"day\":26}}}],\"weekdayDescriptions\":[\"ponedjeljak: 11:00 – 21:00\",\"utorak: 11:00 – 21:00\",\"srijeda: 11:00 – 21:00\",\"četvrtak: 11:00 – 22:00\",\"petak: 11:00 – 22:00\",\"subota: 16:00 – 22:00\",\"nedjelja: Zatvoreno\"]},\"primaryType\":\"restaurant\",\"shortFormattedAddress\":\"One Maritime Plaza, #100, San Francisco\",\"reviews\":[{\"name\":\"places/ChIJU00uDM6BhYAR_ZOluZ0m4qA/reviews/ChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSURucDR1UHR3RRAB\",\"relativePublishTimeDescription\":\"prije tjedan dana\",\"rating\":5,\"text\":{\"text\":\"Bar Sprezzatura skriveni je dragulj u srcu San Francisca koji nudi nezaboravno iskustvo objedovanja nadahnuto ležernom elegancijom Italije. Od trenutka kada uđete unutra, bit ćete prebačeni u svijet živih boja, izvrsnog dizajna i besprijekorne usluge.\\nJelovnik prikazuje izvrstan izbor cicchettija i impresivnu vinsku kartu. Ne propustite priliku kušati njihove prepoznatljive koktele, stručno pomiješane s raznim talijanskim alkoholnim pićima i likerima. Atmosfera je savršena za romantičnu večeru, ležeran izlazak s prijateljima ili čak posebnu prigodu.\\nJedan od vrhunaca bara Sprezzatura je njihova zapanjujuća terasa s koje se pruža prekrasan pogled na okolicu. To je idealno mjesto za uživanje u ležernom obroku ili čaši vina dok upijate kalifornijsko sunce. Bilo da ste ljubitelj talijanske kuhinje ili jednostavno tražite jedinstveno iskustvo objedovanja, Bar Sprezzatura morate posjetiti. La\",\"languageCode\":\"hr-HR\"},\"originalText\":{\"text\":\"Bar Sprezzatura is a hidden gem in the heart of San Francisco, offering an unforgettable dining experience inspired by the casual elegance of Italy. From the moment you step inside, you're transported to a world of vibrant colors, exquisite design, and impeccable service.\\nThe menu showcases a delightful selection of cicchetti and an impressive wine list. Don't miss the opportunity to sample their signature cocktails, expertly mixed with a variety of Italian spirits and liqueurs. The atmosphere is perfect for a romantic dinner, a casual night out with friends, or even a special occasion.\\nOne of the highlights of Bar Sprezzatura is their stunning patio, which offers breathtaking views of the surrounding area. It's the ideal spot to enjoy a leisurely meal or a glass of wine while soaking up the California sunshine. Whether you're a fan of Italian cuisine or simply looking for a unique dining experience, Bar Sprezzatura is a must-visit. La\",\"languageCode\":\"en\"},\"authorAttribution\":{\"displayName\":\"chef_mike510\",\"uri\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/109289857875442298030/reviews\",\"photoUri\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXuZIksWTqkb_MOZITonKIETN7TOPs1T0Z5PhjRe_eflGJH3L-X=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4\"},\"publishTime\":\"2024-10-11T00:55:34.653925Z\"},{\"name\":\"places/ChIJU00uDM6BhYAR_ZOluZ0m4qA/reviews/ChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSURyLS1PdndRRRAB\",\"relativePublishTimeDescription\":\"prije 3 mjeseca\",\"rating\":5,\"text\":{\"text\":\"Izvanredan! Nevjerojatna pića nevjerojatna usluga nevjerojatna atmosfera. Ne mogu reći dovoljno o ovom mjestu. Jedva čekam odvesti sve svoje posjetitelje Intowna ovamo na jelo. Svidjelo nam se sve u vezi s ovim prekrasnim restoranom, bilo da ste domaći ili turist. Ovo je neophodno za svakoga. kakav dragulj ima ovaj grad! Fernando je bio najbolji konobar ikad, a hostesa nas je dočekala s personaliziranom čestitkom za godišnjicu i čašom šampanjca. Ambijent je prekrasan, a posebni dodaci koje dodaju čine ovo ne samo obrokom, već iskustvom koje se uvijek iznova ponavlja.\",\"languageCode\":\"hr-HR\"},\"originalText\":{\"text\":\"Outstanding! Amazing drinks amazing service amazing atmosphere. I can't say enough about this place. Can't wait to take all my Intown visitors here to eat. We loved everything about this beautiful restaurant whether you're a local or a tourist. This is a must for anyone. what a gem the city has! Fernando was the best waiter ever and the hostess crew welcomed us with a personalized anniversary card and glass of champagne. The ambience is beautiful and the special touches they add make this not just a meal but an experience repeating over and over again.\",\"languageCode\":\"en\"},\"authorAttribution\":{\"displayName\":\"Stephanie Hall\",\"uri\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/114648082223539694700/reviews\",\"photoUri\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUcueYoApHQMDPWLSfmK2zzsfoZGN4DXQpJx1fStHxyGYUZbGyD3w=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo\"},\"publishTime\":\"2024-07-20T17:15:28.110942Z\"},{\"name\":\"places/ChIJU00uDM6BhYAR_ZOluZ0m4qA/reviews/ChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSURueDV1MXZ3RRAB\",\"relativePublishTimeDescription\":\"prije tjedan dana\",\"rating\":5,\"text\":{\"text\":\"Bože, kakvo iskustvo.  Naš poslužitelj, Jim, donio je tonu zabave i znanja na stol i nismo mogli biti sretniji.  Svratili smo na ručak i ne razumijem zašto nemaju red ispred vrata.  Kokteli su bili početak onoga što ću ovo nazvati događajem, jer nazvati ga samo ručkom, ovo iskustvo neće biti pravedno. Svaki Jimov prijedlog bio je pun pogodak i potpuno je promijenio naše iskustvo.  Pizza, mesne okruglice, espresso martini, ramini burrata (kuharski poljubac) sve je bilo ukusno, a Jim nas je dokrajčio tostom uz šampanjac. Bilo je to prekrasno iskustvo u cijelosti.\",\"languageCode\":\"hr-HR\"},\"originalText\":{\"text\":\"Oh my goodness, what an experience.  Our server, Jim brought a ton of fun and knowledge to the table and we could not have been happier.  We stopped in for lunch and I don't understand why they don't have a line out the door.  The cocktails were the start of what I'm going to call this an event, because calling it just lunch, will not do this experience justice. Every suggestion Jim made was a hit and totally changed our experience.  The pizza, the meatballs, the espresso martinis the ramini burrata (chef's kiss) all delicious and Jim finished us off with a champagne toast. It was a delightful experience all the way around.\",\"languageCode\":\"en\"},\"authorAttribution\":{\"displayName\":\"Nestor and Michelle\",\"uri\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/106573584272617414046/reviews\",\"photoUri\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUkjMhmq5IWVClHgdyIE6fDH3YL0Qni9vcVUSfdcEie2wtZHRQS=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6\"},\"publishTime\":\"2024-10-10T21:50:41.286321Z\"},{\"name\":\"places/ChIJU00uDM6BhYAR_ZOluZ0m4qA/reviews/ChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUNYeUxlbXR3RRAB\",\"relativePublishTimeDescription\":\"prije tjedan dana\",\"rating\":5,\"text\":{\"text\":\"Došao sam ovamo na događaj i probao sam mnogo predjela!\\n\\nIzdvajamo:\\n- Unutra je prekrasno, ambijent je besprijekoran i ima puno mjesta za sjedenje\\n- Svidjeli su mi se tost s gljivama, izmućena jaja i druge mogućnosti tosta - toliko okusa u jednom malom komadu kruha!\\n- Ljubazno osoblje i ja smo dobili gaziranu vodu koja je bila dobra uz sve ostale grickalice koje sam dobio\\n\\nOpćenito, uživao sam u ovdašnjoj atmosferi i mogućnosti da probam mnogo različitih predjela.\",\"languageCode\":\"hr-HR\"},\"originalText\":{\"text\":\"Came here for an event and got to try a lot of the appetizers!\\n\\nHighlights:\\n- It's beautiful inside, the ambiance is impeccable and lots of places to sit\\n- I liked the mushroom toast, the deviled eggs and the other toast options here - so much flavor in one small piece of bread!\\n- Nice staff and I got a sparkling water which was nice in addition to all the other snacks I got\\n\\nOverall, I enjoyed the vibes here and getting to try a lot of different appetizers.\",\"languageCode\":\"en\"},\"authorAttribution\":{\"displayName\":\"Jenny Xu\",\"uri\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/106691688587887105240/reviews\",\"photoUri\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjULT350ZDJCqi51b8fWIaZc0HmnGkXYxNsLJs01pwQGID39xSN9rg=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6\"},\"publishTime\":\"2024-10-12T18:27:48.165665Z\"},{\"name\":\"places/ChIJU00uDM6BhYAR_ZOluZ0m4qA/reviews/ChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSURyNzgtVVlBEAE\",\"relativePublishTimeDescription\":\"prije 3 mjeseca\",\"rating\":5,\"text\":{\"text\":\"Pronalaženje ovakvog mjesta je razlog zašto se stalno vraćamo u SF. Grad je, baš kao i ovo mjesto, vrlo živ i napredan. Imali smo jednu od najupečatljivijih večera koje smo imali u posljednje vrijeme, hrana, kokteli, usluga i hrana!\\n😙\U0001f90c Sam restoran je tako lijep prostor, namijenjen je da dođete i ostanete neko vrijeme. Potpuno je obnovio našu ljubav prema kulinarskoj sceni SF-a.\",\"languageCode\":\"hr-HR\"},\"originalText\":{\"text\":\"Finding a spot like this is the reason we keep coming back to SF. The City, just like this spot, is very much alive and thriving. We had one of the most memorable dinners we’ve had in a while, the food, the cocktails, the service, and the food!\\n😙\U0001f90c the restaurant itself is such a beautiful space, it’s meant for you to come and stay for a while. It’s totally renewed our love for SF’s culinary scene.\",\"languageCode\":\"en\"},\"authorAttribution\":{\"displayName\":\"Marisa\",\"uri\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/112006762001205739701/reviews\",\"photoUri\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUbj1Q7sq-OEegxoKW7sd9IZhSmEkX_vrFvEbTD2ecci281osclNQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5\"},\"publishTime\":\"2024-07-21T14:55:46.963994Z\"}],\"photos\":[{\"name\":\"places/ChIJU00uDM6BhYAR_ZOluZ0m4qA/photos/AdCG2DN23vgpM7eN_jTEEXBdtVGlOAQ5aiXalsRF29nMwyNqsvWm1whxNodn3mNLy-dRlLrV984Yz6As_VFHQ5brku_lSASafhroGPXtxUYbFbtUT9PEPkELHnk9a2LJEH8rsCUHJ61CH6kh4fFbOits_6RYRPWXrypxet48\",\"widthPx\":2048,\"heightPx\":1152,\"authorAttributions\":[{\"displayName\":\"Bar Sprezzatura\",\"uri\":\"https://maps.google.com/maps/contrib/108913662538193696555\",\"photoUri\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUChbqtdeQ6d7MqNBQF7k5pWGiE8hG6kJST3d-uFNjOl6c3Et