aps.google.com/maps/contrib/108913662538193696555\",\"photoUri\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUChbqtdeQ6d7MqNBQF7k5pWGiE8hG6kJST3d-uFNjOl6c3EtA=s100-p-k-no-mo\"}]},{\"name\":\"places/ChIJU00uDM6BhYAR_ZOluZ0m4qA/photos/AdCG2DMmLFqTvgZtKAHyx8-ksUeEK61KzsLxBY-WFABabcxfONrle-pCWVhkywBKoXDxZkaD1yh9GRRJ-ipogpaPsNfRfLTH56LjmffbH6pti-WUF0pBAgWCvJK66s2oozhtS29T37N_y7p13bzagEb33tw77763zOB5D7WT\",\"widthPx\":1000,\"heightPx\":1296,\"authorAttributions\":[{\"displayName\":\"Bar Sprezzatura\",\"uri\":\"https://maps.google.com/maps/contrib/108913662538193696555\",\"photoUri\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUChbqtdeQ6d7MqNBQF7k5pWGiE8hG6kJST3d-uFNjOl6c3EtA=s100-p-k-no-mo\"}]}],\"outdoorSeating\":true,\"liveMusic\":false,\"menuForChildren\":true,\"servesCocktails\":true,\"servesDessert\":true,\"servesCoffee\":true,\"goodForChildren\":false,\"allowsDogs\":false,\"restroom\":true,\"goodForGroups\":true,\"goodForWatchingSports\":false,\"paymentOptions\":{\"acceptsCreditCards\":true,\"acceptsDebitCards\":true,\"acceptsCashOnly\":false,\"acceptsNfc\":true},\"parkingOptions\":{\"paidGarageParking\":true},\"accessibilityOptions\":{\"wheelchairAccessibleEntrance\":true,\"wheelchairAccessibleRestroom\":true,\"wheelchairAccessibleSeating\":true},\"generativeSummary\":{\"overview\":{\"text\":\"Authentic Venetian cuisine and cocktails are served at this sophisticated bar and restaurant.\",\"languageCode\":\"en-US\"},\"description\":{\"text\":\"Acclaimed restaurant and cocktail bar in the Financial District offering authentic Italian cuisine for lunch and dinner.\\nThe menu features Venetian delights, including cicchetti and risotto, alongside wine and cocktails. People recommend the meatballs, the charcuterie board, and the tiramisu.\\nSet in a unique location, the cozy haunt features a cute coat closet and a gender-neutral restroom. Guests say the staff is attentive, helpful, and fun.\\nCustomers typically spend $50–100.\",\"languageCode\":\"en-US\"},\"references\":{\"reviews\":[{\"name\":\"places/ChIJU00uDM6BhYAR_ZOluZ0m4qA/reviews/ChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUN4ektUd2ZREAE\",\"relativePublishTimeDescription\":\"prije godinu dana\",\"rating\":4,\"text\":{\"text\":\"Sjajno iskustvo, vrlo primamljiva atmosfera i udoban namještaj. Osoblje je bilo vrlo ljubazno i ​​od pomoći u objašnjavanju jelovnika. Uživali smo u ručku od 2 slijeda. Cicchetti su bili izvrsni - definitivno uzmite mesne okruglice! Naša glavna jela su bila dobra, ali vrlo slana. Ali svakako preporučujem 👌\",\"languageCode\":\"hr-HR\"},\"originalText\":{\"text\":\"Great experience, very inviting atmosphere and cozey furniture. Staff were very friendly and helpful with explaining the menu. We enjoyed the 2 course lunch. The cicchetti was delicious - definitely get the meatballs! Our mains were good, but very salty. But would definitely recommend 👌\",\"languageCode\":\"en\"},\"authorAttribution\":{\"displayName\":\"rebekka schnitter\",\"uri\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/110856384598592752041/reviews\",\"photoUri\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIlCQqNpIKgN3IfUEXNJYnPtTtfc2HjYeqYl9S2f-lVcl5OXw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo\"},\"publishTime\":\"2023-05-12T04:16:54.709882Z\"},{\"name\":\"places/ChIJU00uDM6BhYAR_ZOluZ0m4qA/reviews/ChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUNKbm96YmNBEAE\",\"relativePublishTimeDescription\":\"prije godinu dana\",\"rating\":5,\"text\":{\"text\":\"Umjetničko djelo! Ovdje je sve bilo dobro promišljeno. Sviđa mi se atmosfera ulaska u restoran. Čini se kao da si vraćen u prošlost. Na vratima su ga dočekale dvije ljupke dame. Pogledajte slatki ormar za kapute, obožavate! Mjesto za sjedenje bilo je vrlo udobno, velikodušno s jastucima. Serveri su bili fenomenalni, imali smo Andreasa, bio je jednostavno nevjerojatan. Vrlo pažljivi i divni s preporukama. Probali smo od svega pomalo. Bez sumnje favorit je bila daska s mesnatim mesom i rižoto. Naš stol nije bio ljubitelj spritzera, ali imaju pun bar pa svakako naručite svoje omiljeno piće. Prekrasne rodno neutralne kupaonice. Posjetit ću ih ponovno zbog jelovnika za ručak!\",\"languageCode\":\"hr-HR\"},\"originalText\":{\"text\":\"A work of art! Everything was well thought out here. Love the atmosphere of entering the restaurant. Feels like you're set back in time. Greeted at the door by two lovely ladies. Check out the cute coat closet, adorbs! The seating was very cozy, generous with pillows. Servers were phenomenal, we had Andreas, he was simply amazing. Very attentive and wonderful with the recommendations. We tried a little of everything. Hands down favorite was the charcuterie board and the risotto. Our table was not a fan of the spritzers but they have a full bar so definitely order your favorite drink. Beautiful gender neutral bathrooms. Will visit again for their lunch menu!\",\"languageCode\":\"en\"},\"authorAttribution\":{\"displayName\":\"N'Dozie Matingou\",\"uri\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/100874090599933689845/reviews\",\"photoUri\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVDR0PRAAmCrnctquqROmcYid5_RGySaA7PPeQ5zggixDs11jN3Qw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6\"},\"publishTime\":\"2023-06-27T19:44:20.067662Z\"},{\"name\":\"places/ChIJU00uDM6BhYAR_ZOluZ0m4qA/reviews/ChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUR4LW9HTWFBEAE\",\"relativePublishTimeDescription\":\"prije godinu dana\",\"rating\":5,\"text\":{\"text\":\"Jedno od najposebnijih i najaktivnijih iskustava u San Franciscu. Osjećaj je kao da ste u talijanskom salonu u Rimu. Prekrasan dodatak gradu na vrlo jedinstvenoj lokaciji.\",\"languageCode\":\"hr-HR\"},\"originalText\":{\"text\":\"One of the most special and transportive experiences in San Francisco. It feels as if you are in an Italian lounge in Rome. A wonderful addition to the city in a highly unique location.\",\"languageCode\":\"en\"},\"authorAttribution\":{\"displayName\":\"Chris Tompkins\",\"uri\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/104775253861243421931/reviews\",\"photoUri\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVZ-D1tc2skmv23DD0hZKbNIvKNW--H11OM5jmx5Hxz26Oay45VBg=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo\"},\"publishTime\":\"2023-06-06T19:57:25.505396Z\"},{\"name\":\"places/ChIJU00uDM6BhYAR_ZOluZ0m4qA/reviews/ChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUR4Z0t1ZTdBRRAB\",\"relativePublishTimeDescription\":\"prije godinu dana\",\"rating\":5,\"text\":{\"text\":\"Prekrasan interijer! Visoka klasa i kvalitetna usluga. Savršeno za proslavu godišnjice ili poslovnog sastanka. Malo skupo, ali vrijedno iskustva. Hrana i piće bili su vrlo dobri. Publika je starija, pa definitivno nije mjesto za jeftini happy hour.\",\"languageCode\":\"hr-HR\"},\"originalText\":{\"text\":\"Gorgeous interior! High class and quality service. Perfect for celebrating an anniversary or business meeting. A bit pricey but worth the experience. Food and drinks were very good. Crowd skews older so definitely not a place to get cheap happy hour.\",\"languageCode\":\"en\"},\"authorAttribution\":{\"displayName\":\"tynasia hammond\",\"uri\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/117509806960617146806/reviews\",\"photoUri\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKMdhzt_3dfy4Edp9l0KdWKUO_Dl0FpF-ES4wAhrNU_Ne8ycg=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo\"},\"publishTime\":\"2023-05-30T07:03:39.722490Z\"},{\"name\":\"places/ChIJU00uDM6BhYAR_ZOluZ0m4qA/reviews/ChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUN4LWRybmhBRRAB\",\"relativePublishTimeDescription\":\"prije godinu dana\",\"rating\":5,\"text\":{\"text\":\"Prekrasan bar s najnevjerojatnije zabavnim osobljem.  Vino i hrana prekrasni su venecijanski užitak.  Carlo i njegov tim imaju program pića svjetske klase koji oduševljava sva osjetila. Ovo morate posjetiti. Najbolji u gradu.\",\"languageCode\":\"hr-HR\"},\"originalText\":{\"text\":\"Beautiful bar with the most amazing fun staff.  Wine and food are wonderful Venetian driven delights.  Carlo and his squad have a world class beverage program that plays to all senses. This is a must go to. Best in the city.\",\"languageCode\":\"en\"},\"authorAttribution\":{\"displayName\":\"Jerry Young\",\"uri\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/100753233024288059091/reviews\",\"photoUri\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVknE_fKW4VRi6fFTkMJ0PB20DVf5qL85Xo1XJ-6fctoRaqSC_IRg=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5\"},\"publishTime\":\"2023-05-21T15:37:12.635438Z\"}]}},\"addressDescriptor\":{\"landmarks\":[{\"name\":\"places/ChIJLTY_UGCAhYARqvWB2GQTfns\",\"placeId\":\"ChIJLTY_UGCAhYARqvWB2GQTfns\",\"displayName\":{\"text\":\"One Maritime Plaza\",\"languageCode\":\"en\"},\"types\":[\"establishment\",\"point_of_interest\"],\"spatialRelationship\":\"AROUND_THE_CORNER\",\"straightLineDistanceMeters\":38.37008,\"travelDistanceMeters\":47.824673},{\"name\":\"places/ChIJT11eOWCAhYAR_z3tvyd03G0\",\"placeId\":\"ChIJT11eOWCAhYAR_z3tvyd03G0\",\"displayName\":{\"text\":\"The Punch Line San Francisco\",\"languageCode\":\"en\"},\"types\":[\"establishment\",\"night_club\",\"point_of_interest\",\"store\"],\"straightLineDistanceMeters\":68.5253,\"travelDistanceMeters\":198.90771},{\"name\":\"places/ChIJKfpyiGCAhYARNyu9cCeqEbk\",\"placeId\":\"ChIJKfpyiGCAhYARNyu9cCeqEbk\",\"displayName\":{\"text\":\"Safeway\",\"languageCode\":\"en\"},\"types\":[\"bakery\",\"establishment\",\"florist\",\"food\",\"grocery_or_supermarket\",\"point_of_interest\",\"store\",\"supermarket\"],\"straightLineDistanceMeters\":147.23344,\"travelDistanceMeters\":216.30766},{\"name\":\"places/ChIJZ4xOxGSAhYARXvksnJ83SGo\",\"placeId\":\"ChIJZ4xOxGSAhYARXvksnJ83SGo\",\"displayName\":{\"text\":\"Club Quarters Hotel Embarcadero, San Francisco\",\"languageCode\":\"en\"},\"types\":[\"establishment\",\"lodging\",\"point_of_interest\"],\"straightLineDistanceMeters\":137.69197,\"travelDistanceMeters\":221.53961},{\"name\":\"places/ChIJG4kUEWGAhYARtQwQFYlJCio\",\"placeId\":\"ChIJG4kUEWGAhYARtQwQFYlJCio\",\"displayName\":{\"text\":\"Embarcadero Center\",\"languageCode\":\"en\"},\"types\":[\"establishment\",\"point_of_interest\",\"shopping_mall\"],\"straightLineDistanceMeters\":111.04679,\"travelDistanceMeters\":185.28682}],\"areas\":[{\"name\":\