\"hour\":14,\"minute\":30},\"close\":{\"day\":6,\"hour\":17,\"minute\":30}}],\"weekdayDescriptions\":[\"ponedjeljak: 14:30 – 18:30, 21:00 – 23:00\",\"utorak: 14:30 – 18:30, 21:00 – 23:00\",\"srijeda: 14:30 – 18:30, 21:00 – 23:00\",\"četvrtak: 14:30 – 18:30, 21:00 – 23:00\",\"petak: 14:30 – 18:30\",\"subota: 14:30 – 17:30\",\"nedjelja: 14:30 – 17:30, 21:00 – 23:00\"],\"secondaryHoursType\":\"HAPPY_HOUR\"}],\"primaryType\":\"steak_house\",\"shortFormattedAddress\":\"One Market Plaza, 1 Market St Suite M3, San Francisco\",\"reviews\":[{\"name\":\"places/ChIJzcayqEyBhYARyvjdWRk5_0E/reviews/ChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSURuaDhxbjdnRRAB\",\"relativePublishTimeDescription\":\"prije tjedan dana\",\"rating\":5,\"text\":{\"text\":\"Imao sam sjajno iskustvo u STK Steakhouseu! Odmah smo sjeli jer nije bilo previše gužve, što je bio ugodan početak. Atmosfera je bila lijepa i živa, a glazba je bila savršene glasnoće — tiha i groovy, što je pridonosilo ukupnoj atmosferi mjesta.\\n\\nNaručio sam pirjana goveđa kratka rebra koja su došla s krumpirom u kremi. Govedina je bila savršeno začinjena, mekana i ukusna. Kremirani krumpir bio je izvrstan i savršeno je nadopunjavao kratka rebarca.\\n\\nZa piće sam uzeo Savršenu Margaritu, i definitivno je opravdala svoje ime - ne prejaka, ali upravo prave ravnoteže okusa.\\n\\nNaš konobar je bio vrlo pažljiv, redovito se prijavljivao bez pretjeranog ponašanja. Nikada se nismo osjećali zapostavljeno ili užurbano, što je omogućilo opušteno iskustvo objedovanja.\\n\\nSve u svemu, STK Steakhouse me impresionirao svojom hranom, ambijentom i uslugom. Sigurno ću se vratiti ili posjetiti neki drugi dok sam na drugom mjestu.\",\"languageCode\":\"hr-HR\"},\"originalText\":{\"text\":\"I had a great experience at STK Steakhouse! We were seated right away since it wasn’t too busy, which was a pleasant start. The atmosphere was nice and vibrant, and the music was at the perfect volume — low and groovy, adding to the overall vibe of the place.\\n\\nI ordered the Braised Beef Short Rib, which came with creamed potatoes. The beef was seasoned perfectly, tender, and flavorful. The creamed potatoes were delicious, complementing the short rib perfectly.\\n\\nTo drink, I had the Perfect Margarita, and it definitely lived up to its name — not too strong, but just the right balance of flavors.\\n\\nOur waiter was very attentive, checking in regularly without being overbearing. We never felt neglected or rushed, which made for a relaxed dining experience.\\n\\nOverall, STK Steakhouse impressed me with its food, ambiance, and service. I’ll definitely be back or visit another one while in a different location.\",\"languageCode\":\"en\"},\"authorAttribution\":{\"displayName\":\"Derrick Scott\",\"uri\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/112056570603606186922/reviews\",\"photoUri\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUmU3KyC4Su73Bj-HFF8YNVxQCADrEWHDzEZgxyMqxM1GpmMQULnw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5\"},\"publishTime\":\"2024-10-10T18:25:43.936980Z\"},{\"name\":\"places/ChIJzcayqEyBhYARyvjdWRk5_0E/reviews/ChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUNYcHZ1bjdnRRAB\",\"relativePublishTimeDescription\":\"prije tjedan dana\",\"rating\":5,\"text\":{\"text\":\"Moja sestra, moji roditelji, teta i ja otišli smo ovamo na večeru nakon duge vožnje do FSR-a iz drugog grada. Izvrsna hrana i izvrsna usluga. Pozdravite Hakeema koji je bio naš poslužitelj. Bio je vrlo pažljiv i od pomoći. Hvala što ste pitali o alergijama na hranu prije nego što smo naručili i provjerili kod kuhara kako bi se prilagodili ograničenjima vezanim uz hranu/prehranu. Odlične preporuke za piće. Topla preporuka!\\n\\n(Isprike. Dobio sam samo fotografiju janjetine. Odresci su pojedeni prije nego što sam uspio napraviti obavezne slike hrane 😂)\",\"languageCode\":\"hr-HR\"},\"originalText\":{\"text\":\"My sister, my parents, auntie and I went here for dinner after a long drive back to SFO from out of town. Excellent food and excellent service. Shout out to Hakeem who was our server. He was very attentive and helpful. Thanks for asking about food allergies before we ordered and checking in with the chefs to accommodate food /dietary restrictions. Great drinks recommendations. Highly recommend!\\n\\n(Apologies. I only got a photo of the lamb rack. The steaks were devoured before I could do the mandatory food pics 😂)\",\"languageCode\":\"en\"},\"authorAttribution\":{\"displayName\":\"elleRK17 grrr\",\"uri\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/100929659739797872585/reviews\",\"photoUri\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUoxZzqZLfFHicxLMAmUigApI8uS2Aq_5kAIbtTW92xYLr6S8PZ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo\"},\"publishTime\":\"2024-10-16T02:39:34.179588Z\"},{\"name\":\"places/ChIJzcayqEyBhYARyvjdWRk5_0E/reviews/ChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUNya0tDQTVnRRAB\",\"relativePublishTimeDescription\":\"prije 3 mjeseca\",\"rating\":5,\"text\":{\"text\":\"Imali smo najbolje iskustvo u STK-u na 1 Market St. Naletjeli smo na ovo mjesto dok smo kasno jedne večeri šetali Financijskom četvrti. Bilo je to jedno od rijetkih mjesta koje je otvoreno nakon 22 sata, a od 22 do 23 sata bio je happy hour, što je bilo ugodno iznenađenje.\\n\\nDekor je bio prilično zadivljujući i moderan, a mjesto je imalo sjajne vibracije čak i u taj kasni sat. Bio je to upravo onakav kasnonoćni pronalazak kakvom smo se nadali.\\n\\nOdmah smo sjeli, a osoblje je bilo pažljivo i uslužno. Proveli su nas kroz jelovnik, objasnili sretni sat i dali izvrsne prijedloge o opcijama jelovnika.\\n\\nZapočeli smo s Not Your Daddy’s Old Fashioned i Fade to Blackberry — oba toplo preporučujemo. Budući da je bilo kasno, bili smo jednostavni i jeli smo tater tots, kolač od rakova i biftek. Sve je bilo savršeno skuhano i apsolutno ukusno.\\n\\nSve u svemu, toplo preporučujem STK, posebno ako tražite kasnu večeru.\",\"languageCode\":\"hr-HR\"},\"originalText\":{\"text\":\"We had the best experience at STK on 1 Market St. We stumbled upon this place while walking around the Financial District late one evening. It was one of the only places open after 10 p.m., and there was a happy hour from 10-11 p.m., which was a pleasant surprise.\\n\\nThe decor was quite stunning and modern, and the place had great vibes even at that late hour. It was exactly the kind of late-night find we were hoping for.\\n\\nWe got seated right away, and the staff was attentive and helpful. They walked us through the menu, explained the happy hour, and made great suggestions on menu options.\\n\\nWe started with a Not Your Daddy’s Old Fashioned and the Fade to Blackberry—both highly recommended. Since it was late, we kept it simple and had the tater tots, crab cake, and skirt steak. Everything was cooked perfectly and absolutely delicious.\\n\\nOverall, I highly recommend STK, especially if you’re looking for a late-night dinner.\",\"languageCode\":\"en\"},\"authorAttribution\":{\"displayName\":\"Barney Abramson\",\"uri\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/101461389211019198270/reviews\",\"photoUri\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU2j4RldtcFJ1MT5JEmz0amzABE28mjlSQTLCIQCYqJ3CrT83y3=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4\"},\"publishTime\":\"2024-07-03T06:37:31.955554Z\"},{\"name\":\"places/ChIJzcayqEyBhYARyvjdWRk5_0E/reviews/ChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUNIOTR1ZElnEAE\",\"relativePublishTimeDescription\":\"prije mjesec dana\",\"rating\":5,\"text\":{\"text\":\"Z je bio najbolji konobar ikada! Moje rođendansko iskustvo bilo je bolje od bilo kojeg drugog konobara kojeg sam imao. Toliko razmišljanja i na svako moje pitanje imao je odgovor. Vrhunska usluga i atmosfera. 10/10 bi se vratio samo zbog svog iskustva i pažnje posvećene detaljima!\",\"languageCode\":\"hr-HR\"},\"originalText\":{\"text\":\"Z was the best waiter ever! Made my birthday experience was beyond anyone other waiter I have had. So much thought and any question I had he’s had an answer. Exquisite service and atmosphere. 10/10 would come back just for his experience and attention to detail!\",\"languageCode\":\"en\"},\"authorAttribution\":{\"displayName\":\"Beatriz Ramirez\",\"uri\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/112794733174160700540/reviews\",\"photoUri\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUJyoflsy8eYoM6eg1XdMUvKScSEU9x1U3QOuuu6k-biQaMTpY=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo\"},\"publishTime\":\"2024-09-10T05:30:05.622816Z\"},{\"name\":\"places/ChIJzcayqEyBhYARyvjdWRk5_0E/reviews/ChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUNyeEk2UnRnRRAB\",\"relativePublishTimeDescription\":\"prije 2 tjedna\",\"rating\":5,\"text\":{\"text\":\"Izašla sam, nisam bila sigurna kamo želim ići. Pa sam krenuo prema zgradi trajekta. Završio u STK zbog specijala koji sam vidio s pločnika. Znam da sam rekao u drugom postu da sam završio s potragom za izvrsnim hamburgerima. Pa, ovaj je drugi od najboljih koje sam imao. Definitivno je niske cijene, ali savršeno. Wagyu burger i pomfrit za 9,99 dolara nečuveno. Dakle, ako ste vani i dole pored zgrade trajekta, idite STK. Nemojte čak ni gubiti vrijeme ili novac na onom drugom mjestu u zgradi trajekta. Sigurno ću se vratiti. Palac gore 👍. Jučer sam došao s prijateljem na njegov rođendan i kupio ručak. Oboje smo naručili poseban burger, a vikendom se drugačije dodaje slanina i jaje po istoj cijeni. Nevjerojatno\",\"languageCode\":\"hr-HR\"},\"originalText\":{\"text\":\"I went out, not sure where I wanted to go. So I headed towards the ferry building. Ended up at STK because of the special I saw from the sidewalk. I know I've said in another post that I'm done looking for great burgers. Well, this one comes in second to best I've had. It's definitely priced low ,but perfect. A Wagyu  Burger and fries for $9.99 unheard of. So if you are out and down by the ferry building, go by STK. Don't even waste your time or your money at that other spot in the ferry building. I will definitely be going back. Thumbs up 👍. I came with a friend yesterday for his birthday and bought lunch. We both ordered the special burger the different on the weekends is the add bacon and an egg for the same price. Amazing\",\"languageCode\":\"en\"},\"authorAttribution\":{\"displayName\":\"Chef Tony\",\"uri\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/107813554259316757255/reviews\",\"photoUri\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU0C7_RwZtlwTcHw7Cx0yIT_Kfy-ln-8c5H8qptznHvLrAuTuVZ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4\"},\"publishTime\":\"2024-10-06T18:16:14.432049Z\"}],\"photos\":[{\"name\":\"places/ChIJzcayqEyBhYARyvjdWRk5_0E/photos/AdCG2DNewUzbpGEQYg9gkmVwe933NEHASXCv1oUHFZ0WYAHga0ExzKmBVtY9aXQfHs0cRWI8LtgZq0yvGXedujNgTg1_MLuhLojaT1bMJwd8VKm-oIqfLVxa8IodKcR1n6Owjt_3ESVyFLtxehDTDh1qWKxqONzWaAeesvRZ\",\"widthPx\":2048,\"heightPx\":1365,\"authorAttributions\":[{\"displayName\":\"STK Steakhouse\",\"uri\":\"https://maps.google.com/maps/contrib/107219732911202792126\",\"photoUri\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUDGoXYB-7m7aAl1_6IdxzZxTb3UMEes6JOdtSk7YgNnDa6wVg=s100-p-k-no-mo\"}]},{\"name\":\"places/ChIJzcayqEyBhYARyvjdWRk5_0E/photos/AdCG2DOW11vqCGiUfaBk64XIGMfJvOHqxYqfOqOKODBhRI0eCO4ogdnDLoSk0ySJdYT0qYF4ncdk1auL3ngIa7xzQAPRzqqbEf0_jGsxia78P8xufBfAaiynZ-Sq3hwDKFEXWkGk6N2ffOlC8dqSMWquwYOBzBByWB0LwjJQ\",\"widthPx\":2048,\"heightPx\":1536,\"authorAttributions\":[{\"displayName\":\"STK Steakhouse\",\"uri\":\"https://maps.google.com/maps/contrib/107219732911202792126\",\"photoUri\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUDGoXYB-7m7aAl1_6IdxzZxTb3UMEes6JOdtSk7YgNnDa6wVg=s100-p-k-no-mo\"}]},{\"name\":\"places/ChIJzcayqEyBhYARyvjdWRk5_0E/photos/AdCG2DPqWIs_KVtjyu2p7IYqjHJbNdy-SYs1bftwqw9px0tyZMqhcumAwsP_x91V1WzUnr0Uj0zUrqeyIPFCGFolA32tBUQQfqc7m1xzwa1uRF1iFky_T4ooDxQV836B9UzbGjTdhW1-ryr_AZYH4Gh06WuP1IC2cR_k0JpO\",\"widthPx\":4800,\"heightPx\":3600,\"authorAttributions\":[{\"displayName\":\"Rosemarie De La Melena\",\"uri\":\"https://maps.google.com/maps/contrib/105542522480972537058\",\"photoUri\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU0vrgFZ0XyJo-6lOLHT0XD5bkiI3BJ6Vwv2w5CBnuuzk0dg8vj=s100-p-k-no-mo\"}]},{\"name\":\"places/ChIJzcayqEyBhYARyvjdWRk5_0E/photos/AdCG2DPxpuXlh9vlhlKXFvPOPvAvaSx-qJe3Oqf